type.description:
## In Rain

---


[Block Condition Type](https://apugli.readthedocs.io/en/latest/types/block_condition_types/in_rain).

Checks whether it's raining above a block.

Type ID: `apugli:in_rain`

---

### Example
```json
{
    "type": "apugli:in_rain"
}
```
